'''Sector Delta''' was a district of the mysterious [[Space station/Legends|space station]] known as [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']]. It was the location of a number of various different businesses and services and also served as residence of a number of famous and infamous individuals.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

The most well lnown locations in Sector Delta were the ''[[Death Mark]]'', [[Reenogga Personal Services, Cubed]], the ''[[Rusted Cutlass II]]'', and the ''[[Laughing Sullustan]]''.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)" />

